{
    "name": "Berbalang",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Berbalangs prefer to make their homes within a day\u2019s travel of humanoid settlements. These lairs are well hidden and sometimes protected by other undead creatures. Some berbalangs set themselves up as secluded shamans or wise old crones, using <i>alter self </i>to appear human. Ultimately cowardly, berbalangs rarely attack a settlement directly, preferring to pluck its meals from those who stray too far from civilization. A berbalang stands as tall as a human and rarely weighs more than 100 pounds."
        }
    ],
